{"tid":1377642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬，革命定六大訴求就算？","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:00:58.000Z","uid":261330,"like":146,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b750b5ce5018f6969059d7b3170b62bb623821f5","tid":1377642,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"話說我今日係灣仔返工，打算收工就join大家。得閒同唔少客吹水，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">發現我地宣傳嚴重不足</span>，好多傾向支持我地的人已經唔知我地搞緊咩！！所以越來越少人出尼支持，我都答唔出我地到底係革命定係只係六大訴求就算！！行動吾可以只集中於勇武同行動宣傳，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人民教化都好撚重要！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n如果係革命，</span>唔該聽日開始就係鋪天蓋地的革命宣傳！</span>話比人聽點解我要甘做，話比人聽唔做我地會面對D咩，話比人知年輕人冇將來，話比全世界聽，我地將會搞革命！！到時認同我地自然會加入，其他人對我地用的武力並會有心理準備，自己的心理準備都好重要！！其實好多人仲未做好革命的心理準備，所以即使自己人宣傳都好重要，做好心理準備，武力升級就唔會甘慢！！<br />\n<br />\n如果只係爭取六大訴求，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔刻大家係甘宣傳這兩個月政府做左幾多仆街野</span>，我知佢地做左太多，我地活係自己的同溫層，以為宣傳已經好足夠，但其實仲有好多淺黃仲留緊係反送中D個議題到，有好多人唔會好似我地跟新聞跟得甘貼！宣傳阿大佬，6.9如果吾係宣傳左甘耐邊有甘多人出尼！！港豬個腦好需要時間消化！！爭取六大訴求姐係代表政府讓步就收貨，但要政府讓步係長期戰尼，唔好以為係同溫層post左野就等於宣傳，因為D個世界唔係非藍即黃，仲有一大堆港豬等緊我地轉化！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我的立場係，手足你地揀咩，就做D咩。但我地一定要搞清楚自己爭取緊咩！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求就算</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評"},{"pid":"e0d3c0e770d56146267374b919475d488dc22bc5","tid":1377642,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f148dcc5a51cca8ba540cd49eb6d72dafd788d74","tid":1377642,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"481b8de336b14da2025c5af527137e7c31a0ed27","tid":1377642,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329c1b8b3f4bb2e8492d5eba8b3608cd0d0dcec3","tid":1377642,"uid":246032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a7ce570d05cb7b22900f398b8fdce0eafd1848e","tid":1377642,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ececa2b7633d15af2537cd157a4a089d445c05","tid":1377642,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da58869b00765d03509c4bd5ce01f608b8386617","tid":1377642,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"b723e9e0ee5e64cc946b0774b492f779d8035a06","tid":1377642,"uid":54364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a7638ca55435212a9b3c8fc7e8fa29354429b99","tid":1377642,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"革佢老母"},{"p